35 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
36 join in honoring the life and memory of Essie Frankie Mae Stegall Arnold and express their
37 deepest and most sincere regret at her passing.
38 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
39 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the family of Essie
40 Frankie Mae Stegall Arnold.
